  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_docstructbench_llm-raw-scihub-o.O-j.jcp.2010.12.006.pdf_14_61",
    "text": "Substituting into (48) the vectors k and Ug in polar coordinates (44), and let a = |k|4, this yields the propagation angle p and the propagation speed |g| in terms of a and 0.",
